Class BrokerGUITableModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • javax.swing.table.DefaultTableModel
        • suncertify.client.BrokerGUITableModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel

    public class BrokerGUITableModel
extends javax.swing.table.DefaultTableModel
    The BrokerGUITableModel is the model used in the JTable used in displaying the results of queries in the application main GUI. It extends DefaultTableModel class.
